OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CToday:FMainly dry but rather cloudy
OL,6,Fwith the odd spot of rain possible in
OL,7,Fthe morning. A much cooler day than
OL,8,FFriday especially around coastal
OL,9,Fareas, perhaps some brightness for
OL,10,FUpper Deeside during the afternoon.
OL,11,
OL,12,CTonight:FCloudy with some mist and fog
OL,13,Fpatches, feeling cool in light
OL,14,Fnortherly winds. Some clearer spells
OL,15,Fdeveloping early on Sunday morning.
OL,16,
OL,17,CSunday:FCloudy with some showers
OL,18,Fdeveloping, these will be mostly light
OL,19,Fbut a few sharper showers possible in
OL,20,Fthe afternoon, brighter spells inland.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
